trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of related sections within a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en samling relaterade avsnitt i en konfigurationsfil.

trans-unit.source: Use the ConfigurationSectionCollection class to iterate through a collection of <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSection> objects.
trans-unit.target: Använd klassen ConfigurationSectionCollection ska söka igenom en samling av <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSection>objekt.</xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSection>

trans-unit.source: You can access this collection of objects using the <xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.Sections%2A> property or the <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSectionGroup.Sections%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Du kan komma åt den här samlingen med objekt med hjälp av den <xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.Sections%2A>egenskapen eller <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSectionGroup.Sections%2A>egenskap.</xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSectionGroup.Sections%2A> </xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.Sections%2A>

trans-unit.source: The ConfigurationSectionCollection class is also used in the creation of custom types that extend the <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSection> class.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ConfigurationSectionCollection används också för att skapa anpassade typer som utökar <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSection>klass.</xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationSection>
